score if you use them wisely.

329
00:13:50,850 --> 00:13:54,180
Your credit score is like your
financial reputation showing

330
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:56,700
lenders how reliable you are with money

331
00:13:56,700 --> 00:13:58,170
and with a high score.

332
00:13:58,170 --> 00:14:00,660
You'll have much better options
when it comes to borrowing,

333
00:14:00,660 --> 00:14:03,390
which can save you a ton
of money in the long run.

334
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:05,010
I mean, let's say you are 28

335
00:14:05,010 --> 00:14:06,930
and you are ready to buy your first home.

336
00:14:06,930 --> 00:14:09,210
If you've been using a
credit card responsibly

337
00:14:09,210 --> 00:14:12,390
and building that score up, you
could qualify for a mortgage

338
00:14:12,390 --> 00:14:14,100
with a lower interest rate.

339
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:15,450
That means that more

340
00:14:15,450 --> 00:14:17,730
of your hard earned money
stays in your pocket instead

341
00:14:17,730 --> 00:14:18,810
of going to the bank,

342
00:14:18,810 --> 00:14:21,870
but if you've ignored your
credit score, you could end up

343
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:23,550
with sky high interest rates

344
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:25,830
or even be turned down altogether.

345
00:14:25,830 --> 00:14:28,200
So don't fear credit cards, use 'em

346
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:30,900
to build your credit score,
but keep your balance low

347
00:14:30,900 --> 00:14:32,730
and pay it off every month.

348
00:14:32,730 --> 00:14:35,340
Step four is to create an
additional income stream.

349
00:14:35,340 --> 00:14:38,130
If you're serious about financial freedom,

350
00:14:38,130 --> 00:14:40,800
building an extra income stream is key.

351
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:43,980
Think of your income like
a stool with one leg.

352
00:14:43,980 --> 00:14:45,810
If you're relying on just your job,

353
00:14:45,810 --> 00:14:48,900
that's a single leg holding
you up your entire life.

354
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:51,960
If that leg breaks, let's
say you lose your job,

355
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:54,300
