nothing to keep you steady.

356
00:14:54,300 --> 00:14:56,940
This happens way more
now than it ever used to.

357
00:14:56,940 --> 00:15:00,840
The truth is secure jobs aren't
as common as they once were.

358
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,860
Most people will have

359
00:15:01,860 --> 00:15:04,200
