legs like a side hustle

361
00:15:07,230 --> 00:15:10,290
or investments, that
stool becomes rock solid.

362
00:15:10,290 --> 00:15:11,640
Now, if one leg fails,

363
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:13,650
